#scene.setConv( 'port1', 'Ada_normal' );
Adalais: Okay, I have that book now.
#scene.setConv( 'port1', 'Ada_normal' );
Adalais: The title is "One-Hundred-Thousand Recipes for Pizza".
#scene.setConv( 'port1', 'Ada_annoyed' );
Adalais: Why was this up there?
#scene.setConv( 'por1', 'Ada_thoughtful' );
